description:
This is a 20 minute workout called 'Sleep Easy Knowing Everything Is Going to be OK!  (Guided Meditation)' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Sleep Prep and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This 20-minute guided sleep meditation offers peace and reassurance knowing everything is going to be ok.  By surrendering to the soothing voice and calming music, you can release the weight of your concerns and trust in the inherent goodness of life.  Allow yourself to drift into a deep, restful sleep, knowing that whatever challenges may arise, you possess the strength and resilience to overcome them.  So, if you're seeking a deep restorative sleep, press play and let this guided meditation be your comforting companion through the night.  This is an Original guided  sleep meditation recorded by us.  

A special thank you to all our monthly supporters!  
We appreciate all your support and contribution to allow this channel to continue to share our guided meditations with the world.  Thank you!!!
